    <abstract>
      <t>The BGP Monitoring Protocol (BMP) defines access to only the Adj-RIB- In Routing Information Bases (RIBs). This document updates the BGP Monitoring Protocol (BMP) RFC 7854 by adding access to the Adj-RIB- Out RIBs. It adds a new flag to the peer header to distinguish Adj- RIB-In and Adj-RIB-Out.</t>
    </abstract>
